- Jangan!

97
00:06:46,663 --> 00:06:50,208
Kau selalu memainkan ponsel
beberapa saat ini.

98
00:06:50,291 --> 00:06:51,417
Kau menunggu telepon?

99
00:06:53,544 --> 00:06:54,545
