110
00:07:41,134 --> 00:07:43,302
Itukah makna anak-anak bagi orang tua?

111
00:07:46,597 --> 00:07:48,850
Jika mau tahu, menikahlah.

112
00:07:50,351 --> 00:07:52,228
Jangan hanya bicara, beraksilah.

113
00:07:59,652 --> 00:08:02,280
