154
00:10:40,813 --> 00:10:41,856
Ayah, kita bicarakan.

155
00:10:41,939 --> 00:10:43,858
- Tak boleh ada kekerasan.
- Minggir!

156
00:10:44,358 --> 00:10:45,693
- Jeong-in!
- Jeong-in!

157
00:10:45,776 --> 00:10:46,903
- Ayah!
- Jeong-in!

158
00:10:47,904 --> 00:10:49,447
Ini semua tak ada gunanya.

159
00:10:49,530 --> 00:10:51,282
Di dunia ini, uang yang penting.

160
00:10:51,365 --> 00:10:53,200
Uang memegang kuasa. Seperti itulah.

161
00:10:54,911 --> 00:10:56,078
Sial.

162
00:10:57,955 --> 00:10:59,582
Apa yang tak bisa dibeli?

163
00:11:04,170 --> 00:11:07,048
Uang bahkan bisa beli cinta
dan kasih sayang.

164
00:11:13,179 --> 00:11:14,639
Namun, itu menyedihkan.

165
00:11:17,224 --> 00:11:18,684
Aku akan jujur kepadamu.

166
00:11:21,020 --> 00:11:22,021
