169
00:11:34,492 --> 00:11:36,827
Aku mau istriku

170
00:11:37,954 --> 00:11:40,289
bisa menyombongkan suaminya.

171
00:11:40,373 --> 00:11:41,874
Aku angkuh? Tidak.

172
00:11:43,751 --> 00:11:45,002
