173
00:11:47,004 --> 00:11:48,089
demi cinta.

174
00:11:51,008 --> 00:11:52,301
Karena cintaku kepadanya.

175
00:11:56,931 --> 00:11:59,475
Maka kau harus terus berusaha maju.

176
00:11:59,850 --> 00:12:01,310
Kenapa membatalkan rencananya?

177
00:12:05,439 --> 00:12:06,732
Dasar berengsek.

178
00:12:07,483 --> 00:12:10,236
Kau yang tak memberiku pinjamannya.

179
00:12:15,950 --> 00:12:17,994
Saat ayahku mewariskan gedungnya kepadaku,

180
00:12:18,661 --> 00:12:19,954
